      "translated": "I want to continue watching over and supporting Ena, who has resolved not to give up on her art and her dreams."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "From Niyori-san... \"Ena's heart's color...\" Oh, what a lovely message."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "Thank you so much for saying that my vocal performance brought it to life so vividly."
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "I'm the one who should be thanking you for receiving it that way."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": "I always hope that Ena's feelings will reach everyone."
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "Of course, she's a game character, a 2D being,"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "but Ena is truly alive. And since no one knows"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "what her future holds yet,"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "I want to deliver something that feels real."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "Thank you for such a kind message. It makes me very happy."
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "All right."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "Anyway, I have so much to talk about. If I keep chatting here,"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "I'll run out of time in five minutes."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "So let's move right along."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "I've picked out some scenes I personally want to talk about,"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "so let's watch them together."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "I was a bit selfish today with the selection."
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "The staff are shaking their heads when I say \"selfish,\" but..."
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "I really struggled to choose."
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "I honestly wanted to watch"
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "from episode 1 to 8 with you all."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "But for now,"
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "let's look at episodes 7 and 8."
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "This is an AfterTalk, so I'll be talking quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": "If you find me too noisy,"
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "please go back and watch the story in the game later."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "Let's get started."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "Episodes 7 and 8."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "Here we go."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "No way!"
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": "What?"
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "She's calmed down."
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "I think she knew deep down all along."
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "She's deleting her account... she's not hacked."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": "Ena has made so many resolutions, but... wait, what does this mean?"
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "With her selfie account,"
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": "she used it as a way to escape or rely on others."
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "That's true."
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": "But she couldn't run away."
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "She wants to go to the exhibition."
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "translated": "But she didn't have the resolve to tell those around her yet."
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "translated": "She acted like"
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "translated": "it wasn't a big deal, but this time,"
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "translated": "she's actually quitting and making a real decision."
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "translated": "It's painful from here on, but it feels like the fog in her heart has cleared."
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "translated": "I acted this out with a mix of relief and the weight of what's to come."
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "translated": "In the end, I felt like Ena was finally at peace."
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "translated": "The reason I chose episodes 7 and 8 is because of her father."
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "translated": "They've been through a lot, and there were times she couldn't face him, but she really admires him. As she hit puberty and things happened, and since her dad isn't great with words, she ended up hiding her respect for him out of frustration. But as she grew as an artist, she remembered those feelings. That's why I got to voice young Ena too. As a child, she was so pure, and everything was new and sparkling. Her father was in that world,"
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "translated": "and to her, he was an idol—someone who creates amazing things."
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "translated": "I imagined her talking to someone"
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "translated": "who was like a mass of pure light."
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "translated": "I acted while feeling the sheer greatness of the art her father creates."
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "translated": "Because of that, I could transition into the drawing scene without losing that sparkle."
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "translated": "Being able to draw happily while embracing that feeling was a huge moment for me."
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "translated": "It was significant."
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "translated": "And for the first time, she could clearly say, \"It's fun.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "translated": "For Ena, she's finally reached this point."
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "translated": "She's still on her journey, but she finally made it here."
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "translated": "Oh, I'm gonna cry."
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "translated": "This is bad."
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "translated": "When I first saw the script at home, I cried so much."
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "translated": "I was just so happy for her."
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "translated": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "translated": "This is a total broadcast accident."
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "translated": "Um..."
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "translated": "It's been five years—well, not five years in Ena's timeline—but there's so much history there."
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "translated": "I think many of you find Ena's story very relatable."
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "translated": "Since I'm also in a world of art where there are no \"correct\" answers,"
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "translated": "I really understand her."
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "translated": "But more than that, seeing Ena's hard work"
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "translated": "finally start to pay off... well, \"pay off\" is a simple way to put it, but..."
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "translated": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "translated": "I was so happy that I cried for her as Minori Suzuki, thinking \"Congratulations!\""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "translated": "And while reading, I felt Ena's relief that she finally made it here."
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "translated": "She could finally feel a simple emotion. That tension she's been carrying finally snapped."
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "translated": "Ah, sorry... I have plenty of tissues here."
    }
  ]
}

